d enhanced generalization across projects and development phases. By grounding augmentation in real-world failure modes and model introspection, this method advances the state-of-the-art beyond heuristic or blind augmentation techniques, offering a principled, interpretable, and scalable solution for industrial-grade software quality assurance tools.",
